              "text": "Show off your quick reaction skills by slicing fruits that pop up from the bottom of the screen. Although each fruit gives you the same number of points, you can earn bonus points if you chop multiple fruits with a single swipe. The game doesnâ€™t come with a timer. This means that you can play Fruit Chop for hours and go on scoring points! Your objective is to score more than the competition."
